                                             int ubu)
        Parameters:

        lbu - lower bound (inclusive) of the universe
        ubu - upper bound (inclusive) of the universe
        Returns:
        the complement of this set wrt to universe set [lbu, ubu]. Values smaller than lbu and greater than ubu are ignored.
